entries.femaleVariant: You Sergei?
You Sergei?
Nice of you to ask. Lately I feel like there is neon sign over my head that says, "Sergei who fuck with Tyger Claws."
Give me the coordinates.
You don't seem especially nervous.
How did you piss off the Tyger Claws?
All right, then. Fling me the coordinates.
Don't seem so nervous, for a man in your situation.
How'd you piss off the Tyger Claws?
Ah, but you see, I'm in "home stretch" now.
Ah, it was just a... friendly misunderstanding.
<mothertongue l="rus" m="Gospodi" b="And he also have little dog. " a=", what kind of hitman goes around with dog?"/>
Present's the car?
It's a bit more than ordinary car, but in nutshell – yes.
Mm. Sure.
I open door to garage. It open from inside, too. Just in case.
Just a moment.
Wakako sent me.
Wakako sent me.
I have little present for Tyger Claws sitting in garage.
Ah, so you are my knight in shining armor.
My name is Sergei.
V.
Oh, well, call me "S" then.
One base away from freedom!
How're you so sure that the Tyger Claws'll accept you present?
entries.maleVariant: How're you so sure the Tyger Claws will accept you present?

entries.femaleVariant: Oh trust me, I know. We Russians have very refined intuition about such things.
And you are just... delivery girl.
entries.maleVariant: And you are just... delivery boy.

entries.femaleVariant: This man, he look normal – beard, brown shoes... nothing, y'know, breathtaking.
This "misunderstanding" involve you shooting him?
It was worse – much worse. Bah! I say too much already!
Just drive it there and they take care of the rest.
And don't mess this up, huh? I count on you!
